287
00:12:34,799 --> 00:12:35,759
write it down the way I said.

288
00:12:44,519 --> 00:12:45,559
Let's hope the next round

289
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:47,000
goes off smoothly.

290
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,480
The next one will absolutely be fine.

291
00:12:48,799 --> 00:12:50,200
To guarantee Su Yang passes

292
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:51,240
the luck test smoothly,

293
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:53,120
I specifically set up a deadly shooting game.

294
00:12:53,519 --> 00:12:54,759
Inside this revolver,

295
00:12:55,039 --> 00:12:56,159
there's only one paint bullet.

296
00:12:56,399 --> 00:12:57,519
I had someone load the paint bullet

297
00:12:57,639 --> 00:12:58,759
into the third chamber.

298
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:00,840
And his opponent shoots first.

299
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:02,360
No matter what,

300
00:13:02,759 --> 00:13:03,720
Su Yang wins.

301
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:06,879
Nicely done.

302
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:09,279
The one on the right goes first.

303
00:13:23,279 --> 00:13:24,120
I have to say,

304
00:13:24,639 --> 00:13:25,799
you're really unlucky.

305
00:13:26,399 --> 00:13:27,279
My luck

306
00:13:27,639 --> 00:13:28,679
has always been incredibly good.

307
00:13:29,399 --> 00:13:31,000
For luck-based games like this,

308
00:13:31,639 --> 00:13:32,519
to me,

309
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:34,879
it's no different from an open-book exam.

310
00:13:47,919 --> 00:13:50,159
I feel like my luck's always been pretty good too.

311
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:52,159
I was planning to fire four shots in a row.

312
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:54,080
One shot each.

313
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:55,519
You never said that.

314
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:09,200
Hold on.

315
00:14:10,159 --> 00:14:11,679
Is he out of his mind?

316
00:14:12,039 --> 00:14:13,600
It was supposed to be one shot each.

317
00:14:13,600 --> 00:14:14,799
Is he playing games here?

318
00:14:14,879 --> 00:14:15,519
And you.

319
00:14:15,759 --> 00:14:16,399
You.

320
00:14:16,879 --> 00:14:18,759
You could've put the bullet in the first chamber,

321
00:14:18,759 --> 00:14:20,279
and let Su Yang win right away!

322
00:14:21,039 --> 00:14:21,679
I...

323
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:23,600
How am I supposed to write this?

324
00:14:26,759 --> 00:14:27,720
Just write...

325
00:14:28,759 --> 00:14:29,639
Su Yang

326
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:32,159
would rather sacrifice himself

327
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:34,600
than let his opponent face danger.

328
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:35,519
Highly responsible.

329
00:14:35,679 --> 00:14:36,559
Full of conviction.

330
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:38,039
He perfectly fulfilled

331
00:14:38,039 --> 00:14:40,559
all the duties and obligations of a captain.

332
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:41,840
Got it.
